[38;5;141m> [0mNow let me address the HIGH-priority findings (S1, A1, A2, S2) in the main recipe. These go in the Cross-Cutting Design Points section. Let me add S1 (voiceprint governance) after the "Audio is PHI" paragraph, A1 (layered faithfulness) expanding the existing faithfulness paragraph, A2 (per-cohort monitoring) expanding the existing paragraph, and S2 (behavioral-health 42 CFR Part 2) expanding the existing behavioral-health paragraph:[0m[0m
